==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: buffalo soldier
<hw>buffalo soldier</hw> <def>A black soldier of the United States army
who served in the American west in the late 1800's, often as an indian
fighter, and usually as part of an all-black troop; -- the name was
given by the indians due to their their kinky hair, and the name was
believed also to be a compliment on their courage.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

